25cff","tid":1015702,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"你隻耳仔有冇事？(甩皮等等的問題)<br />\n頭有冇痕？<br />\n會唔會好多耳屎？<br />\n<br />\n皮膚病有好多種<br />\n而且病徵都好相似(紅，痕)<br />\n例如我記得睇書見過的有：<br />\n脂漏性皮膚炎 <br />\n過敏性皮膚炎<br />\n接觸性皮膚炎<br />\n異位性皮膚炎<br />\n有咩分別我已經唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過建議你可以去圖書館睇本&ldquo;內外科護理學&rdquo;(冇得借走)<br />\n<a href=\"https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/lib/item?id=chamo:3422187&amp;fromLocationLink=false&amp;theme=WEB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebcat.hkpl.gov.hk%2Flib%2Fitem%3Fid%3Dchamo%3A3422187%26fromLocationLink%3Dfalse%26theme%3DWEB&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=b303afa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://webcat.hkpl.gov.hk/lib/item?id=chamo:3422187&amp;fromLocationLink=false&amp;theme=WEB</a><br />\n入面有講好多病的病徵同護理方法<br />\n常見的過敏原 病發的部位等等<br />\n<br />\n本書信唔信得過我唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都可以睇下先"},{"pid":"71959760984b422f0a264a908e33ef8ad7b3f542","tid":1015702,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4f199f8638c6ba81477b2020d48658f27711d0f","tid":1015702,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dd73931728c4e5e0a830c2edf0f9bfeb17f6b4e2","tid":1015702,"uid":43613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"可以試下比錢check敏感源, 睇下係咪純粹敏感<br />\n<br />\n如果濕疹, 就唔洗理佢啦, 反正醫唔好<br />\n平時食野清D, 唔好飲咁多糖, 唔好食辣野<br />\n另外唔好揸類固醇, 就咁樣算啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"係 成日生暗瘡 <br />\n睇醫生食抗生素 一粒都冇<br />\n一停又生 打算食a酸 但食緊其他藥<br />\n醫生唔俾食a酸 之後發現自己係食物敏感<br />\n食包就出事 半日即出瘡 食粒敏感藥 <br />\n瞓醒退曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"食完敏感藥成日迷迷痴想瞓覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1f4297c49b08f2519f60657f34ca19aaf3c740","tid":1015702,"uid":71166,"like":1,"disl